title: titus_3rd_season_complete_dvd_rips
description:
Complete third season of Titus ripped from DVDs. 480X320, English with no subtitles.

NOTE: Episode 21, "The Protector," was a late entry and wasn't intended to be the series finale. You might want to position this before episode 18, "The Visit," which begins the story arc that concludes with episode 20, "Insanity Genetic Part 2."

I freaking loved this show. It helped me realize my family wasn't the only crazy family out there. Chris, screw your politics, but I really, really dig your show. Love ya, man.
